name: SPT Frozen Green Peas
description: High-quality frozen green peas from SPT, cleaned and packed to retain freshness.
Perfect for use in pulao, curries, pav bhaji, sabzis, salads, and snacks.
Frozen at peak freshness to preserve natural sweetness, color, and nutrition.
Saves preparation time with no peeling or shelling required.
Each pack contains 500 g of ready-to-cook green peas.
keyBenefits: Ideal for a variety of Indian dishes
Saves prep time in the kitchen
